shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>Minecraft Yourscraft Hiscraft Herscraft Itscraft</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507989880,"created_at":1507989880,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47831","user":{"id":"333185","nickname":"Treubler","avatar_url":"https://creation.codemao.cn//490/YW5kXzEwMDFfMzMzMTg1XzBfMTY5MTg5OTU0NTM5OV9EU3lLZUZZWg==.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>@|糖醋排骨| MCSM基本上就是故事书，你基本上没发hold剧情。</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507989812,"created_at":1507989812,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47569","user":{"id":"235327","nickname":"力言菌","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/15956682634391.gif","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><a rel=\"nofollow\">プログラム銅鑼焼</a>&nbsp;你这跟没说一样<br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507903755,"created_at":1507903755,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47556","user":{"id":"256641","nickname":"****","avatar_url":"https://static-user-center.codemao.cn/user_0006.png","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>好玩的游戏我有五大标准：</p>\n<p>1、有可玩性，值得去玩</p>\n<p>2、BGM节奏感强</p>\n<p>3、视觉效果顶呱呱</p>\n<p>4、不抄袭，不照抄</p>\n<p>5、素材到位（最后一个，算吗？）</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507900848,"created_at":1507900848,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47554","user":{"id":"333185","nickname":"Treubler","avatar_url":"https://creation.codemao.cn//490/YW5kXzEwMDFfMzMzMTg1XzBfMTY5MTg5OTU0NTM5OV9EU3lLZUZZWg==.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>我爱MC！！</p>\n<p>剧情：作者太太来搞，本来没有</p>\n<p>规则：还是作者太太定。</p>\n<p>难易：又是作者定太太定。</p>\n<p>音画：一部分看材质包，一部分看作者太太。</p>\n<p>这么说来，MC也是：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font size=\"7\" color=\"#ff0000\">编 程 软 件</font></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507900525,"created_at":1507900525,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47501","user":{"id":"214296","nickname":"主播喵副本","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FmnbCWV2OzmsQSOnJc8r6Tte5W25","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>我比较喜欢模拟生存类的</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507897157,"created_at":1507897157,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47494","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>能从中学到东西的游戏是好游戏</p>\n<p>问题是现在的人不都喜欢好游戏</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507894737,"created_at":1507894737,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47493","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><a rel=\"nofollow\"></a><a href=\"http://codetank.alloyteam.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://codetank.alloyteam.com/</a></p>\n<p>这个就不错</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507894638,"created_at":1507894638,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47492","user":{"id":"235327","nickname":"力言菌","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/15956682634391.gif","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>中国人的游戏，也就是“充钱送豪礼”之类的，太过于急功近利了。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>像《阴阳师》，做细节做的细致入微，让宅男们乖乖掏钱</p>\n<p>同意！！！！</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507893822,"created_at":1507893822,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47491","user":{"id":"101954","nickname":"胡咚咚","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/a015bcb7-f868-4895-a24c-2410e4d13147","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>有好的剧情，丰富的内容，可以保存数据不丢失（备份数据至网络这种），对，就是这样</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507893800,"created_at":1507893800,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47490","user":{"id":"235327","nickname":"力言菌","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/15956682634391.gif","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>——摘自《gamecores》可以摘抄？？？？</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507893764,"created_at":1507893764,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47488","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>如果我们将人类玩游戏的过程，用强化学习的概念去表达，会分成四个阶段：</p>\n<ol>\n <li>观察自己的角色在游戏中的状态（State）。比如DOTA中，你看到了你的金币超过了一个想要 购买的装备的价格。比如守望先锋中，你看到了你的终极大招的进度条已满。</li>\n <li>根据上面获得的状态，你现在会根据一定的策略（Policy）来选择行为（Action）。比如DOTA中，你可以在金币达到数量的时候立马购买想要的装备，也可以等待合适的时机来决定是否要购买更高级的装备。在守望先锋中你也有同样的选择，是选择现在就直接释放大招，还是等待合适的时机。</li>\n <li>在选择行为之后，你就会执行行为。你可能发现等待时机是一个很好的行为，因为大部分新手会立马去买装备或者释放大招，而老练的玩家会等待合适的时机。无论如何，选择的行为都会获得回报（Reward）。比如立即释放大招的回报可能是一个都没有杀死，也就是回报为0，而等待合适的时机去释放大招杀死了5个人，也就是回报为5。回报可以有不同的定义，有些人觉得团灭对方是一件很爽的事情，但是有些人只是为了赢得比赛。</li>\n <li>玩家在观察到自己的行为产生的回报之后，会调整自己的策略，从而采取未来回报最高的行为。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>这四个阶段的不断循环，就是一个人玩游戏并不断练习自己的技巧的过程。当然这个过程还可以描述的更复杂一点，比如一个人会有计划的去执行自己的想法，会根据当前的状态去评估整体的局势，从而采取不同的策略。但是总的来说离不开这四个重要的概念，状态（State），策略（Policy），行为（Action），回报（Reward）。这里就不使用公式什么来解释专业的知识了，主要的目的还是为了通俗易懂。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ——摘自《gamecores》</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507893504,"created_at":1507893504,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47487","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>中国人的游戏，也就是“充钱送豪礼”之类的，太过于急功近利了。</p>\n<p>像《阴阳师》，做细节做的细致入微，让宅男们乖乖掏钱</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507893408,"created_at":1507893408,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47486","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>我们回头看看，唯一一个超过一千个小时的游戏也就是DOTA了</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507893344,"created_at":1507893344,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47485","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>我觉得游戏设计要好</p>\n<p>但这不代表素材要好（当然画风很重要）</p>\n<p>像暴漫风格就很受人喜爱，因为他刚好与现代人简单喵的生活理念吻合。</p>\n<p>包括我所有的作品，风格就是“往酸菜里面加牛奶”（老鱼头语）</p>\n<p>游戏设计包括很多：</p>\n<p>1.规则设计：好玩的游戏这些做的非常极端。</p>\n<p>要嘛是只给你一个框架好很少很少的限制，让你自己发展（例如《我的世界》还有编程猫），这样会产生大量的趣味，故而好玩。</p>\n<p>要么是规则做的很紧，但是获得胜利的方式可以自由开辟，比如你在王X峡谷推塔时可以做很多事情。</p>\n<p>还有一种特殊的，就是规则简单但是你能做的也单一，是用来打发时间的（例如《开心消消乐》《贪吃蛇》），这些就像是鸡肋，弃之可惜，食之无味。</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507893275,"created_at":1507893275,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47479","user":{"id":"235327","nickname":"力言菌","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/15956682634391.gif","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>编程猫虽然只有创造，没有破环，但是。。。。。。。。啥时候可以出个破坏codemao网站的功能，我想看codemao混乱ui的样子啊哈哈哈哈哈！！！！！！！！！！！！！&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>我好坏啊</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507891449,"created_at":1507891449,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47478","user":{"id":"235327","nickname":"力言菌","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/15956682634391.gif","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>Minecraft也超级不错的，自主创造，破坏，什么都能满足你只要你想得到没有你做不到！！！！！虽然没有剧情但是，创造与破坏成为了Minecraft的一大亮点！<br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507891346,"created_at":1507891346,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"47477","user":{"id":"235327","nickname":"力言菌","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/15956682634391.gif","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>我一直在思考，为何有人把王者荣耀删了又下回来，这款游戏有毒吧，能把人毒死，现在的人虚荣心太多，玩个游戏总是喜欢比谁的皮肤多，谁杀人多，自己xxxxxxxxxxx666啊什么的，别人杀你一次你要杀他10次，竞争力太强。其次就是这个游戏在人脉圈发展起来了，只要看见朋友玩，自己就要玩。这就是戒不掉“毒药”的原因吧？<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/b6/doge_thumb.gif\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/emoji/codemao/4.gif\">不过我也喜欢玩的，但是不希望大家砸钱太多，毕竟是个游戏嘛</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":150